{"tid":1320852,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"7月17日老人遊行, 至今未獲「不反對通知書 」","createTime":"2019-07-15T13:26:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-15T15:15:20.000Z","uid":134071,"like":34,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"b49cfd78c0eb227a264bc02888b3cbd8fdae9c82","tid":1320852,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T13:26:20.000Z","msg":"莫非真係暫停發出「不反對通知書 」?<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190715/59826721\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190715%2F59826721&d=mMU56kjTNdUxye0JV9HIjatywrPEU2nSstxgUPIv8k8%3D&h=a8e9bed3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190715%2F59826721&h=e537639b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190715/59826721</a><br />\n<br />\n 2019年07月15日<br />\n【逆權運動】「銀髮族」7.17靜默遊行往政總撐年輕人 至今未獲不反對通知書 <br />\n<br />\n反送中運動遍地開花，但市民的訴求卻始終如一，都是希望政府能回應民間五點訴求，明言「撤回」惡法，就連一班「銀髮族」也要為修例發聲。「香港銀髮族靜默遊行」將於星期三（17日）下午5時正由遮打花園遊行到政府總部，要求政府正面回應民間的五項訴求，不過警方至今仍未發出不反對通知書。<br />\n<br />\n是次活動的申請人楊女士強調他們並無任何政黨聯繫，認為過往如6.12遊行期間，她只是以支持者的身份參加，並無自發去舉辦活動支持一群年輕人，在7.1遊行期間雖有以義工身份擺街站，但她坦言當時仍不支持年輕人包圍立法會，認為暴力不能解決問題。直至她看到年輕人進入立法會的片段後，只破壞一些象徵性的東西而非任意破壞，她有感年輕人只是願意為這個社會、香港付出代價，直指「社會上仍然有部份人對年輕人唔了解」，又指近期有不少年輕人輕生，故她今次選擇站出來，希望給予他們支持，同時鼓勵其他「銀髮族」一同站出來。<br />\n<br />\n退休教師譚先生指他們已事先聯絡共18位救護人員包括7名護士、2名醫生及9名急救人員，但由於他們仍未收到警方發出的不反對通知書，故未能確定當日能為遊行人士提供急救服務。譚指摘警方遲遲未發出不反對通知書，並表明他們早於上星期二已提交申請書，星期五亦已討論雙方都能接受的遊行路線，不明白他們仍未收到不反對通知書的原因。譚解釋近日一連串的社會運動源於政府制度不公，又指現時泛民在立法會處於弱勢，加上連串的DQ事件，令市民的聲音未能直達議會。 <br />\n<br />\n前社會福利總幹事孫先生慨嘆社會上不斷以「邊青」、「隱青」、「憤青」或「廢青」標籤年輕人，但他直指現時上述的標籤已不再適用於年輕人身上，應以「心水青」形容他們，強調港府應加強理解年輕人的需要。<br />\n<br />\n前社會工作者麥先生指現時港府不少房屋、教育等福利均由民間及一群熱血青年推動政府策劃，強調他們的行動都是有「純正」動機及原因。麥亦指摘警方需反省近期執法時的失控行為及情緒，須「有過必改」。<br />\n<br />\n主辦方預計屆時會有1,500人參與遊行，料遊行約1.5小時完成。主辦單位又提醒參加者需帶備足夠水，穿白衫黑褲，可帶同自製的示威牌前往。遊行隊伍屆時將以1.5米乘20米長的橫額，寫上「反對制度暴力 我要真普選」並沿遮打花園，經終審法院、皇后像廣場、太子大廈、金鐘廊和連儂牆，而終點設為政府總部。"},{"pid":"1bca8cc1b86237f2e915179250d53d5f8d5d9bda","tid":1320852,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T13:27:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e32e38d6cc692c5c337fddacfbdf10c486efddd","tid":1320852,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T13:27:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad4afc37a1ffe78d51e3e7590135b9cfb336304a","tid":1320852,"uid":263423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T13:29:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"91c11630dfda1611a96ee0580bc41a3c35eaa2e2","tid":1320852,"uid":213607,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T13:30:13.000Z","msg":"怕拐杖有暗器<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d0e53cdef0b66231e294a1cb6b0281944f0f754","tid":1320852,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T13:31:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a89b594cac4141a1d6ac4fcdcbd9dd361889991e","tid":1320852,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T13:31:35.000Z","msg":"唔好意思阻大家<br />\n<br />\n［建制議員應總辭］39嘆冷氣逗人工議員拎光環譴責暴力，何君堯關鍵缺席聯署<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1320529\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1320529</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"2905f5f8d236e87bbb5e2576bfca82ab64b48a96","tid":1320852,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T13:32:12.000Z","msg":"指各區遊行釀警民衝突 蔣麗芸倡停批不反對通知書<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1318640/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1318640/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"eae310de1cdcd3f65571de2319c44aff2dd5fe29","tid":1320852,"uid":261699,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T13:32:41.000Z","msg":"老人家都怕?<br />\n唔撚係掛班警犬<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aaa4d533ca1a8303a3e0ec6969872fbf654557ad","tid":1320852,"uid":69746,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T13:33:05.000Z","msg":"如警務處處長沒有在本條例所指明的時限內，按照第(2)款發出、張貼或發布反對遊行通知，即當作警務處處長已發出不反對公眾遊行通知<br />\n詳見公安條例14（4）"},{"pid":"3d0a38ec734fe73a884f82864590a3a538f0b626","tid":1320852,"uid":15084,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T13:35:42.000Z","msg":"廢老同廢青都可以we connect <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大和解"},{"pid":"2cc5c43f40a3188ca26a88f804651a77dcfb4525","tid":1320852,"uid":66822,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T13:46:09.000Z","msg":"政府最驚老嘢<br />\n撞到少少都上頭版 <br />\n當時又要道歉<br />\n又民意逆轉又盛"},{"pid":"f64ccd490ce27907dd9f07e7606826083f0c4be8","tid":1320852,"uid":92448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aaa4d533ca1a8303a3e0ec6969872fbf654557ad","tid":1320852,"uid":69746,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T13:33:05.000Z","msg":"如警務處處長沒有在本條例所指明的時限內，按照第(2)款發出、張貼或發布反對遊行通知，即當作警務處處長已發出不反對公眾遊行通知<br />\n詳見公安條例14（4）"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T13:49:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a517cc088b49521c1af04a4771c7a5fe543048c7","tid":1320852,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T13:50:16.000Z","msg":"唔批係咪唔行得先？夠膽拉埋班老人家囉on9犬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2dd391d143afeac47af024b81a21dcb1a476a856","tid":1320852,"uid":53612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T13:51:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"122e9af7e5d278baccc15378be9fa95177ee0080","tid":1320852,"uid":264124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T13:52:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd3b6e155c01549c2fe1ed73398ee65c69d378fb","tid":1320852,"uid":108337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T13:53:41.000Z","msg":"睇電影呢，支杖可以係矛 可以係槍<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好危險架"},{"pid":"b361df5a27fafa56e5da24674265677934e43058","tid":1320852,"uid":201356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T14:39:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FOcSKU8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFOcSKU8.jpg&h=c01ff97a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>【反送中】盲人白杖被警方質疑是攻擊性武器　失明人協進會：非常荒謬深感失望<br />\n 10:11 2019/06/14  <br />\n<br />\n特區政府修訂《逃犯條例》，觸發市民遊行、罷工罷課包圍立法會及政府總部，向政府表達憂慮，卻引發嚴重警民衝突。香港失明人協進會發出聲明，指有視障人士在港鐵站被警方截停，更質問視障人士使用的白杖是否攻擊性武器，令人覺得荒謬。<br />\n<br />\n香港失明人協進會在facebook專頁發表題為「視障人士的白仗絕非武器」的聲明，指大批香港市民就《逃犯條例》修訂草案，透過和平遊行、罷工罷課包圍立法會及政府總部的方式向政府表達憂慮，只換來警方的暴力對待，實在令人心痛。<br />\n<br />\n該會接獲視障會員告之，於6月9日的大遊行及6月12日的包圍立法會及政府總部行動中，均有不少視障人士參與並表達訴求。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<code>對於警方竟截停視障人士並對白杖的用途有所懷疑，本會深感失望，認為警方必須加強前線警務人員對殘疾人士的認識。</code>"},{"pid":"7a85ea8504aa7de0a4b1ab80d6f96a03af6b035a","tid":1320852,"uid":201356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dd3b6e155c01549c2fe1ed73398ee65c69d378fb","tid":1320852,"uid":108337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T13:53:41.000Z","msg":"睇電影呢，支杖可以係矛 可以係槍<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好危險架"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T14:41:10.000Z","msg":"毅進仔認識<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">零舍不同</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd01c29db6a3c06e54b7e1ad42145830871d1bde","tid":1320852,"uid":172349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T14:41:53.000Z","msg":"打又唔打得，咪唔比你遊行囉"},{"pid":"f901020a089b26d997133c45f56c27dba80e17b3","tid":1320852,"uid":269287,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T14:43:06.000Z","msg":"根據公安條例,只要依足手續比7日通知,就算無接到不反對通知,都可以照行,險4非佢2出信3反對"},{"pid":"1099a815760f5360c87e5f1d18cf594f64195d58","tid":1320852,"uid":269287,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f901020a089b26d997133c45f56c27dba80e17b3","tid":1320852,"uid":269287,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T14:43:06.000Z","msg":"根據公安條例,只要依足手續比7日通知,就算無接到不反對通知,都可以照行,險4非佢2出信3反對"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T14:43:37.000Z","msg":"根據公安條例,只要依足手續比7日通知,就算無接到不反對通知,都可以照行,除非佢出信反對"},{"pid":"77c788372e27e3c7c9aba98911066d15f32fabbb","tid":1320852,"uid":134744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aaa4d533ca1a8303a3e0ec6969872fbf654557ad","tid":1320852,"uid":69746,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T13:33:05.000Z","msg":"如警務處處長沒有在本條例所指明的時限內，按照第(2)款發出、張貼或發布反對遊行通知，即當作警務處處長已發出不反對公眾遊行通知<br />\n詳見公安條例14（4）"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T14:44:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d6abc0a37b03927c2d6c5c951c152a1e93f83984","tid":1320852,"uid":229886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1099a815760f5360c87e5f1d18cf594f64195d58","tid":1320852,"uid":269287,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f901020a089b26d997133c45f56c27dba80e17b3","tid":1320852,"uid":269287,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T14:43:06.000Z","msg":"根據公安條例,只要依足手續比7日通知,就算無接到不反對通知,都可以照行,險4非佢2出信3反對"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T14:43:37.000Z","msg":"根據公安條例,只要依足手續比7日通知,就算無接到不反對通知,都可以照行,除非佢出信反對"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T14:45:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n民主社會真係好<br />\n政府唔係大撚晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9c1f8d52db1f6cb5b32446e2d47670f10660417","tid":1320852,"uid":153311,"like":0,"dislike":0